<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Crosby House" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Crosby House</orth> (Ff) or <orth extent="full" opt="n">Crosby Place</orth> (Qq), a house in Bishopsgate Street, where Richard III lived before his accession: <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.213" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 213</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.345" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 3, 345</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.1.190" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 190</bibl>.
